com.interpss.dstab.dynLoad

Interface DistNetworkEquivalentModel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DistNetworkEquivalentModelImpl

    public interface DistNetworkEquivalentModel
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Dist Network Equivalent Model'. Distribution network equivalent model

    The following features are supported:

    • Mva
    • BSub Station
    • RFdr
    • XFdr
    • TMin
    • TMax
    • Step
    • VMin
    • VMax
    • TDelay
    • TTap
    • RComp
    • XComp
    • FB
    • XXf
    • TFix HS
    • TFix LS
    • LTC
    See Also:
    DStabDynamicLoadPackage.getDistNetworkEquivalentModel()
